  "Snow accumulates on a driveway at rate S(t) = 2 + cos(t) inches per hour and is shoveled at a constant rate of 1.5 inches per hour (for t > 2). Find the net snow depth at t = 4 if S starts at t = 0 and shoveling starts at t = 2.": "",
